title: Sixth suspect arrested, charged in Atlantic City Expressway shootout
content:
To view this page ensure that Adobe Flash Player version 10.2.0 or greater is installed.
Lenardo Caro, 24, of Little Egg Harbor Township; Yahshaun Stukes-Williams, 19, of Mays Landing; Shaun Stukes, 38, of Atlantic City and a 16-year-old boy were injured and were taken to AtlantiCare Regional Medical Center, City Division. They were charged with weapons offenses. The adults also were charged with employing a juvenile in a crime.
